{"article_id":"kft7Wp38fru6J1Vd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein defended the Justice Department ' s handling of the special counsel ' s still-secret report ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Attorney General William Barr is \" being as forthcoming","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"as he can \"","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"about his process","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"for redacting and releasing the roughly 400-page document .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"In his first interview since the conclusion of the special counsel ' s investigation , Mr. Rosenstein beat back suggestions","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that Mr. Barr is trying to mislead the public","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"by releasing only a four-page summary of Robert Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"The attorney general in that letter said","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"the Mueller probe found","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"President Trump and his campaign didn ' t conspire with Russian interference in the 2016 election","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"but reached no conclusion","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"about whether the president obstructed justice .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"With the absence of a recommendation , Mr. Barr and Mr. Rosenstein determined","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s actions weren ' t criminal .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Democrats have demanded access to the full report ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Barr said","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"he would release , likely next week ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"after blacking out portions for sensitive information .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" He ' s being as forthcoming","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"as he can ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and so this notion","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"that he ' s trying to mislead people ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"is just completely bizarre , \"","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein said .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Mr. Barr is under intense pressure","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to quickly produce the edited report amid concerns from Democrats","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that the attorney general , a longtime advocate of executive-branch authority , is seeking to protect the president from politically damaging information","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"the report may contain .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Their worries were heightened after reports","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that some investigators on Mr. Mueller ' s team had told associates in recent days","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that they believe","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"the report is more critical of Mr. Trump on the obstruction issue","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"than Mr. Barr indicated in his summary .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein wouldn ' t say","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"why Mr. Mueller rendered no conclusion on that critical question .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" It would be one thing","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"if you put out a letter","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"and said ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"' I ' m not going to give you the report , ' \"","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein said .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"\" What he said is ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"' Look ,","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"it ' s going to take a while to process the report .","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"In the meantime , people really want to know","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"what ' s in it .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"I ' m going to give you the top-line conclusions. '","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"That ' s all","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he was trying to do . \"","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein , Mr. Barr , their top advisers and a member of Mr. Mueller ' s team have been involved","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"in reviewing the report for material","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"related to intelligence sources , continuing investigations , grand-jury matters and the privacy of individuals","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"not charged with crimes .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein wouldn ' t say","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"how it was going ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"only that the public should have \" tremendous confidence \" in Mr. Barr .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"The rare interview in Mr. Rosenstein ' s fourth-floor office at the Justice Department came in his waning days on the job ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"with the special counsel investigation","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"he oversaw","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"now complete","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"and Mr. Trump ' s nominee","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"to replace him ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Deputy Transportation Secretary Jeffrey Rosen , awaiting confirmation by the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"After nearly 30 years in the department , Mr. Rosenstein , 54 years old , said","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"he doesn ' t know what he will do next ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"only that he hopes to start a new job at the end of the summer .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"His remarks came one day after Mr. Barr said","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"he would form a team","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"to examine the origins of a 2016 counterintelligence investigation","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that conducted what he termed as \" spying \" on people","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"associated with the Trump campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"a characterization","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Democrats and some former Justice Department officials ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"including fired Federal Bureau of Investigation Director James Comey ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"found disturbing .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Speaking at a conference in San Francisco on Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Mr. Comey said ,","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"\" When I hear that kind of language used ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"it ' s concerning ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"because the FBI and Department of Justice conduct court-ordered electronic surveillance .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"I have never thought of that as spying . \"","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"It isn ' t known whether Mr. Barr ' s review will examine any of Mr. Rosenstein ' s actions ,","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"namely that he approved an application","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"to ask a court to grant continued surveillance of former Trump campaign adviser Carter Page ,","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"who had long been on the radar of U.S. counterintelligence for his communications with Russians .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein wouldn ' t comment on Mr. Barr ' s inquiry of that counterintelligence probe ,","depth":4},{"id":89,"text":"but he said generally","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"that he is open to objective scrutiny","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"and stands by his approval of the renewal .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein has been under an unusually intense spotlight as the No . 2 Justice Department official ,","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"largely because of his decision","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"to appoint Mr. Mueller early in his tenure ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"which drew repeated swipes from Mr. Trump and concerns among some of the president ' s advisers","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that he would move to fire the deputy attorney general .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein said","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"he has stayed on the job at Mr. Barr ' s request ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"adding ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"\" for me , it ' s a real privilege . \"","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Early on , at Mr. Trump ' s request , Mr. Rosenstein wrote a memo","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"that the White House initially cited as grounds","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"for firing Mr. Comey .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"On Thursday , he said","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"he stands by the memo","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"and has few regrets about his time in office .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"\" If you put something in writing ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"put your name on it","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"and be prepared to stand behind it , \"","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"\" That ' s been a theme of my career . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":195,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":170,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":117,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":1,"right":115,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":113,"right":114,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":162,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":138,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":126,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":119,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":6,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":121,"right":122,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":9,"right":120,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":14,"r